link:labelLink.link:label: Financial Position 2
Equity Contributed Equity Paid Up Ordinary Share Capital Amount
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of paid-up ordinary share capital issued by the reporting entity and determined in accordance the relevant prudential standard.
Equity Contributed Equity Paid Up Ordinary Share Capital Other Qualifying Instruments Amount

This is the value, as at the relevant date, of paid-up ordinary share capital; or, instruments with the characteristics of ordinary shares instruments issued by the reporting entity that satisfy - as determined by APRA - the eligibility criteria of the relevant prudential standard.
Equity Dividends Paid Or Declared Amount

This is the value for the duration of the relevant period of dividends declared or paid (distributions) out of profits to the shareholders of a company in proportion to their holdings of a particular class of capital.
Equity Reserves Accumulated Comprehensive Income And Other Disclosed Reserves Amount
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of accumulated other comprehensive income and other disclosed reserves, as determined in accordance with relevant accounting standards.
Equity Reserves Accumulated Comprehensive Income Other Reserves Disclosed Other APRA Specified Amount

This is the value, as at the relevant date, of any accumulated other comprehensive income and other disclosed reserves specified by the Australian Prudential Regulation Authority. This item is to be determined in accordance with relevant prudential standards.
Equity Reserves Asset Revaluation Reserve Property Amount
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of the balance of the reserve relating to the revaluation of property, as determined in accordance with relevant prudential standards.
Equity Reserves Available For Sale Reserves Total Amount

This is the value, as at the relevant date, of the reserve in relation to assets classified as available-for-sale, consistent with the classification and measurement basis used in accordance with relevant accounting standards.
Equity Reserves Foreign Currency Translation Reserve Excluding Unrealised Gains Losses FX Hedge Investment For Operation Amount

This is the value, as at the relevant date, of the reserve relating to exchange rate differences arising on a monetary item that forms part of a reporting entity's net investment in a foreign operation in accordance with Australian accounting standards. For the purposes of this item, exclude unrealised gains and losses from a foreign currency hedge of a net investment in a foreign operation.
Equity Reserves Gains Or Losses Cash Flow Hedges Amount

This is the value, at the relevant date, of the reserve in relation to the effective portion of the gain or loss on the cash flow hedging instrument as determined in accordance with Australian Accounting Standards.
Equity Reserves General Reserves Amount
This is the value, as at the relevant date of General Reserves determined in accordance with relevant accounting standards.
Equity Reserves Share Based Payments Reserve Employee Remuneration Package Amount

This is the value, as at the relevant date, for the equity settled share based payment reserve amounts in accordance with relevant Australian Accounting Standards. For the purposes of this item include only payments granted to employees as part of their remuneration package.
Equity Reserves Unrealised Gains Losses Foreign Currency Hedge Investment Foreign Operation Amount

This is the value, as at the relevant date, of the unrealised fair value gain or loss of a hedging instrument that is determined to be an effective hedge of the net investment in a foreign operation, in accordance with Australian Accounting Standards.
